Package com.diogonunes.jcolor

Class Attribute

java.lang.Object
com.diogonunes.jcolor.Attribute
public abstract class Attribute
extends Object
Abstracts ANSI codes with intuitive names. It maps a description (e.g. RED_TEXT) with a code (e.g. 31).
See Also:
Wikipedia, for a list of all codes available, StackOverflow, for a list of codes with examples
